    public static enum MemberCriteria.IterateStrategy
extends Enum<MemberCriteria.IterateStrategy>
    The MemberCriteria.IterateStrategy determines in which order AnnotatedElements are iterated when using an Iterable of AnnotatedElements.
    Since:
    1.0.0;
    Author:
    Ren√© Link [rene.link@link- intersystems.com]
